{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"54382-jasu-na-mpira","title":"Jasu na Mpira","description":"Jasu ni msichana aliyependa kucheza mpira. Lakini hakukuwa na aliyetaka kucheza nae. Jasu alitafuta mbinu!","language":"Kiswahili","langCode":"sw","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Rehema  Egbert"],"illustrators":["Godwin  Chipenya"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/54382-jasu-na-mpira"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/118043/size3/3277f1b45cda0564c0e8837dfd06a280.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/118043/size6/3277f1b45cda0564c0e8837dfd06a280.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96695/size6/aefb46a3bd0cabcced37351dce75f546.jpg","text":"Jasu hakuwa na mpira. Alitamani sana kucheza mpira.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96696/size6/69f5c57721464714c9b38255f3bc56d0.jpg","text":"Jasu aliwaona rafiki zake wakicheza mpira.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96698/size6/d466c84be39cf45b09be256053c91fbc.jpg","text":"Jasu alitafuta soksi, karatasi na kamba. Alitengeneza mpira.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96699/size6/200689ef11d26fe623cbcb15b887d81d.jpg","text":"Mpira ulikamilika.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96701/size6/9877c0642ea0066d810c705a18c7c9ee.jpg","text":"Kila alipokwenda Jasu aliupiga mpira.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96702/size6/82ca195f1825d567fa75ebae255de319.jpg","text":"Alipokwenda kwa babu aliupiga mpira juu. Mpira ulidondosha maembe machanga.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96707/size6/a8e1f0ad888230e18c33fdc7e179e68e.jpg","text":"Babu alimwambia Jasu awe mwangalifu. \nJasu alimwahidi babu kutorudia tena.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96708/size6/abad8ac135f7ec3d8d7eedacaf6e678a.jpg","text":"Jasu alikwenda sokoni na mama yake.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96709/size6/28679a6c08436cf47ec2621bd04d68b6.jpg","text":"Jasu aliupiga mpira.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96710/size6/57f397f74fac309d9189f8b1d63a5741.jpg","text":"Mpira ukamwaga nyanya. \nMama alimwambia Jasu asicheze sokoni.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96711/size6/e082bc38af95c2c8aac79c77ee176496.jpg","text":"Jasu aliomba msamaha.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96712/size6/de8ebc620394dabdc1f50ede9c197bfc.jpg","text":"Jasu alihuzunika. Akaubeba mpira wake hadi nyumbani.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96713/size6/873d758549437252d40dbefff34959bb.jpg","text":"Alipofika, aliwafuata marafiki zake wakacheze uwanjani.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96714/size6/393dfab505fc12114c15957b7b85f647.jpg","text":"Babu alipomwona Jasu akicheza mpira uwanjani. \nBabu alifurahi, akamnunulia Jasu mpira mzuri.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96715/size6/dd9dc49bc30df9c1700319f4db7f588d.jpg","text":"Wote walicheza mpira kwa furaha. \nJasu aligundua kucheza uwanjani ni salama.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96716/size6/84645d62d83b290e122073e718f0ffa1.jpg","text":"17/17","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":106}}